'''''Scientific Galactica''''' was a media publication in the years preceding the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] that dealt with science-related topics.<ref name="DMSH">''[[Darth Maul: Shadow Hunter]]''</ref> Toward the end of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire's]] reign, it claimed to be "the galaxy's leading scientific journal." It employed over 300 researchers and writers, most of which were trained in self-defense and survival.<ref name="SWG:TSD">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=terminal||Tatooine Scientific Defense}}</ref>

In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]],<ref name="SWG_timeline">{{SWG_timeline}}</ref>  a number of its researchers were lost when attacked by creatures in the wild on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. Following this catastrophe, hunters were employed to ensure that such places of research were kept clear of dangerous creatures.<ref name="SWG:TSD" />

[[I-5YQ]] was a reader.<ref name="DMSH" />

